item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

If it was in your moparscape client, it means people were attacking NPCs that shouldnt be attacked, with magic. It is unpreventable, unless the NPCs are made un-attackable, you were probably playing on a dune-scape source, which does this a lot.
